name: LORE CARD 001: The Deep Ones
description:
Our settlers believe themselves to be the only inhabitants of this brave new world when they arrive.  It soon becomes apparent that this is not the case.

Deep in the depths of the planet's oceans something has awakened from its slumber.  Ancient and powerful, it’s far from pleased to have these new creatures crawling on the surface.

As the settlers begin to stake their claim on the planet’s oceans, ships and mechs begin to vanish. There is a tale among sailors of giant sea creatures roaming the oceans.  Creatures with a siren’s call….
